snippet.title: inFAMOUS Second Son - Official E3 Gameplay Video
snippet.description:
inFAMOUS: Second Son is available on March 21, 2014.
http://us.playstation.com/ps4/games/infamous-second-son-ps4.html

Watch the first official gameplay reveal for the PlayStation 4 exclusive, inFAMOUS Second Son from the PlayStation E3 2013 press conference!
